Solace
------

- default shell is groovy
- solace sources all scripts matchings ~/.solace/scripts/*.groovy
- colorschemes should be placed in ~/.solace/colors, following the format:
    $c.colors['color_sheme_name'] = [
        '*':[
            background:'#331211FF',
            foreground:'white',
            caretColor:'green'
        ],
        '*.prompt':[
            background:'#442322FF',
            foreground:'yellow',
        ],
        '*.input':[
            background:'#442322FF',
            foreground:'white',
            caretColor:'green'
        ],
        '*.choice':[
            background:'#664544FF',
            foreground:'yellow'
        ]
    ]
    - selector format is '<SwingComponentName>.<class>'
